    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>About the Weather App</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to our Weather Application! This tool provides real-time weather updates and forecasts for cities around the world. By utilizing the OpenWeather API, our app delivers accurate weather data, including temperature, humidity, wind speed, and weather conditions.
      </p>
      <p>
        The app also allows users to search for specific locations and view weather forecasts for the upcoming days. You can easily access weather information for your current location or any city worldwide.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our goal is to make weather information accessible, reliable, and user-friendly. Whether you're planning a trip, checking local weather conditions, or curious about the forecast, this app helps you stay informed.
      </p>
      <p>
        Technologies used:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
        <li>OpenWeather API</li>
        <li>Node.js & Express (Backend)</li>
        <li>HandleBars (Templating Engine)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
